      • parallelReduce

        public <R extends Reducer<R,T>> R parallelReduce(R reducer)
        Performs a parallel reduction on each local handle of the underlyin DistChunkedList collection before reducing the result of each individual host. This method is blocking and needs to be called on all hosts to terminate.
        Type Parameters:
        R - the type of the reducer used
        Parameters:
        reducer - the reduction operation to perform
        Returns:
        the result of the specified reduction across all local handles of the underlying collection
